data.title: AHRC NYC Foundation
data.meta_description: The AHRC New York City Foundation supports programs for children and adults who have intellectual and developmental disabilities in New York City.
data.text:
There are many ways you can support the AHRC New York City Foundation

Your gifts help sustain our current programs and ensure that these services continue to be available for families who need them.

Impact Stories

To make choices and decisions based on their own aspirations.

Live as independently and be as productive as possible.

Participate fully in their communities.
